Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:29.91,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}You changed me so much I don't remember what I was like before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:34.40,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The breeze caresses our cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:36.51,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Lullaby of Birdland...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:40.73,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}As we run down the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:44.79,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}our flimsy shadows extend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:49.73,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's like a neverending summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:55.24,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It feels like when we snuck into the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:01:01.27,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Yeah, let's swim with our clothes on. Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:03.96,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's an intense spiral of temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:08.48,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}A beat pierces my heart. A strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:12.05,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It vanishes after a quick spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.85,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Even on bad days, I dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:19.84,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}and dance to some swing. The music quickly surrounds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:22.69,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}What is this dance exactly? I can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:31.95,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Don't leave me. It's stuck in my head, and I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:35.04,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:40.83,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}is like love.
