Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:09.76,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:19.16,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:19.78,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.62,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I love the cakes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.10,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:26.66,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is Jun's family's shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:31.16,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:34.96,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.63,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, why don't you come over to my place and watch them practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:48.68,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's over. She hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.55,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What's that, avant-garde?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.73,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come on, Richie. Get your head on straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.11,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}How we gonna have a session?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.49,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Everyone, Yurika is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:05.37,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ri, didn't your dad tell you that outsiders aren't allowed down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:11.49,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika's our friend, so I'm\Nsure Dad won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.50,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yurika, enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.34,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.55,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.55,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to get a little fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.40,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.40,apollon main,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:45.07,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're Sentaro's sister... Sachiko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:46.95,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you playing by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:50.58,apollon main,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. All my friends are off at cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:52.22,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.75,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about we play together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:57.55,apollon main,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:01.70,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:04.43,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not playing? That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:10.93,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's a relic, so sometimes it gets ornery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:14.69,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You just gotta work a little magic on it when it gets like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:22.45,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Jun. How'd that get it to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:24.74,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:29.06,apollon main,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, is this the Children's \NTelephone Counseling Office?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:31.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:37.46,apollon main,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,You see, there's this boy named Hashiguchi who's always mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.96,apollon main,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,He hides my slippers, pulls my hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.44,apollon main,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.16,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:52.84,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You know, maybe that Hashiguchi actually likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:58.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is he wants to be friends with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.63,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but he doesn't know how to express his feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.65,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,so he acts out like that without \Nreally thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.78,apollon main,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,He does not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:11.29,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I made the girl that I really like cry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:13.56,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to apologize to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:16.50,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but even if I do, I don't think she'll forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.50,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.51,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:36.69,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. I can't stay mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.36,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:44.69,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.99,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidentally, I've been going to the shop for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.87,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea it was your family's.
