Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:55.12,apollon main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101311&\bord0\shad0\fnRage Italic LET\fs30\blur0.5\frx8\fry352\pos(598,228)\frz357.293\clip(m 552 209 l 574 213 588 232 672 230 670 185 558 189 546 190)}Shirayuri
